value.0: Greetings prime, welcome to my city of Zanshibon.
By all means, what would you like to know?
Why shouldn't it be?  Does it not fall into your pathetic preconceived notions of the structure of the universe?  Foolish <man/woman>, you must suspend your disbelief to truly open your eyes.
This is unnacceptable to you that we might share an appreciation for beauty?  Oh, spare me your judgement please... you are far too quick to dispense it.
Of course I was.  It was I that pulled you from your planewalking course.  Celestia indeed.. How boring, I can't believe you'd want to go there.
Calm yourself.  I am in need of your aid, if you can believe that.  You have spilled much blood on your homeworld.  You have sent many souls to their resting place.  I need one such as yourself....
It matters not.  I present you with a choice.  Fight the hordes of my rival out in the Abyssal Wastes, or go back home to your precious world, and return to the pitiful measure of your life.
*Sigh* Very well..  If that is your wish.  Go back to your meaningless world.  The white portal shall return you to where I pulled you from, take it if that is your wish.
Good, yes...  Talk to my servant to bind yourself here.  Then, to the Wastes with you.  My rivals gather their forces there.  Slay them all!!  For the Glory of Paush!!

I have some questions for you.
Actually, I changed my mind.  I'll just be going now.
Do you have anything to barter?
Why is this temple so... peaceful?
But...it's so beautiful.  How can we be in the Abyss?
That's it, enough of you.
Perhaps.  Let me ask you some more questions.
You sound like you were expecting me...
So why did you pull me here?  What is going on?  Why me?
Yes, their deaths mean nothing to me.  I kill for the thrill of it.
I want to go home.
I will.
Actually, let me ask you some more questions first.

Very well.  I take my leave now.
